<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
PETROLEUM (PET)
</IN>
<LP>
   PITTSBURGH -- USX Corp. said its program to solicit bids
and sell the exploration and production assets of its Texas
Oil &amp; Gas Corp. subsidiary was concluded.
   Bids were solicited on six geographic packages of
properties and USX expects to conclude transactions resulting
in the sale of three packages. These transactions are
expected to be closed by the end of the third quarter. No
further bids are being solicited for the remaining
properties.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   USX is a steel and energy concern.
</TEXT>
