<LP>
   COASTAL Corp. (Houston) -- Colorado Interstate Gas Co., a
unit of Coastal Corp., said it completed the offering of $180
million of senior debentures, due June 2005, via Shearson
Lehman Hutton Inc. The energy concern said proceeds will be
used for general corporate purposes.
</LP>
